snippet.title: CJ's Elephant Antics Longplay (C64) [QHD]
snippet.description:
Developed by Genesis Software and published by Codemasters in 1991

Awesome platform game originally released   on budget, representing great value for money at the time.

The mission is some: help CJ the elephant escape his captors and return to his family in Africa.

Credits
Coding: Dave Clarke
Graphics: Jonathan Smyth
Music: Ashley Hogg
